snippet.title: the static speaks my name DEVELOPER'S COMMENTARY
snippet.description:
The official developer's commentary for my game 'the static speaks my name.' I discuss everything from making pet shrimp edible to why jacob sits down to pee. If you enjoy this commentary, check out my other game Bucket Detective, available for $4 on Steam including an hour long in-game dev commentary: https://store.steampowered.com/app/461170/Bucket_Detective/
